==Portuguese==

===Verb===
'''beber'''

# (''transitive'') to [[drink]] ([[something]]);
#: "''Ele está '''bebendo''' água.''" - He is drinking water.
# (''intransitive'') to [[consume]] [[alcoholic]] [[beverage]]s;
#: "''João '''bebeu''' muito na festa.''" - John drank a lot in the party.
# (''intransitive'') to [[drink]] something.
#: "''Preciso '''beber'''!''" - I need to drink!

